WEBVTT

01:15:04.067 --> 01:15:07.734
With an unstable hand, if your
signature varies everyday...

01:15:07.900 --> 01:15:09.942
then which of them will I show
in court as your signature?

01:15:10.817 --> 01:15:12.734
Tell me, brother! Tell me!

01:15:17.692 --> 01:15:20.859
How do you hold and
urinate with that hand?

01:15:21.525 --> 01:15:22.567
Will you just let it leak?

01:15:25.609 --> 01:15:26.984
Alright sign it.
